description: Request a batch of multi-part upload or copy pre-signed URLs.

uploadId.description: The unique identifier of a multi-part request.

partNumbers.description: The part numbers to get pre-signed URLs for.

contentType.description: Optional parameter.  When included each pre-signed URL will be signed with the given Content-Type.  This is necessary for clients that must include the header 'Content-Type' with all HTTP GET calls.

partMD5Hex.description: Optional list of MD5 checksums represented as hexadecimal string for each part to check against. If present must match the size of the partNumbers list and will be added as a constraint to the pre-signed URL.
